    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The removal or reduction of acid content by neutralizing the acidic components in a material, often paper, and providing an alkaline buffer to counteract acidic build-up in the future.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
